  </outputs>

  <acceptance-criteria>
    <criterion testable="true">`FileSummarizationService.cs` exists and uses gpt-4o-mini.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Summary output ≤120 chars.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">No log statement carries textContent OR summary text body.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">`dotnet build` + new tests exit 0.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">BFF publish delta &lt;0.5 MB.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">code-review + adr-check exit 0.</criterion>
  </acceptance-criteria>

  <notes>
    Trust framing is task 077's responsibility — this service produces the summary; 077 tells the LLM it is NOT authoritative. The two responsibilities are separated by design (architecture P3).
  </notes>

